Hello. I'm using LG monitor L1900R. It can be controlled only thru ddc (no
OSD menu).
Experimentally I found that the most important controls (brightness 0x10 and
contrast 0x12) are coincide with Samsung SyncMaster 173T. So I can control
them from the command line. But what about others :( ?
As far as I guess the development of ddccontrol is stopped now. But perhaps
someone will check the presented output and update ddccontrol-db for L1900R
monitor? It'll be very nice :)
Thanks ahead!
